rComments: Dr. Hunter really puts you into current engagements concerning the internet and virtual communities. Class is engaging, but heavily relies on participation to make it worthwhile, so I would avoid if not really into talking. Very worthwhile class overall, exams are easy, group project and own research throughout the course of the class.
Dr. Hunter is an awesome teacher.  I learned a lot in the class.  She was helpful and incredibly knowledgeable.

Not clear about the assignments and changes the syllabus once a month or more. Assigns too much reading and assigns powerpoint projects that she neither looks at or grades, ends up wasting your time. Not sure what we were supposed to be learning.
